    "body": "You could try something like:\n\n``` js\nvar app = express();\n\n// Register your REST endpoints\n\napp.use(function(req, res) {\n    res.sendfile(path.join(someBaseDir, req.originalUrl, 'index.html'));\n})\n\n// GET example.com/foo/bar returns (someBaseDir)/foo/bar/index.html\n```\n\nYou'll want to do proper validation, but I think something like this could work for you.\n",
